<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/output.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-950 text-gray-100 font-sans antialiased">

    <!-- ── NAV ── -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-gray-950/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-gray-800">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="text-[#6B72FF] font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">MahitKC</a>
        <a href="/#projects" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Portfolio
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="pt-24 pb-24 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs bg-[#02066F]/30 text-[#6B72FF] border border-[#02066F] px-3 py-1 rounded-full">ASP.NET Core</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-[#02066F]/30 text-[#6B72FF] border border-[#02066F] px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Full-Stack</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-[#02066F]/30 text-[#6B72FF] border border-[#02066F] px-3 py-1 rounded-full">MVC</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Movie Reviews</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-[#6B72FF] font-medium mb-6">ASP.NET Core MVC Admin Application</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="#" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#02066F] hover:bg-[#0309A8] text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">Live Demo</a>
            <a href="#" class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-[#02066F] text-gray-300 hover:text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">GitHub Repo</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Screenshot placeholder -->
        <div class="w-full aspect-video bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-12 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="text-center">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-gray-700 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3 20.25h18a.75.75 0 00.75-.75V6a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75H3a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v13.5c0 .414.336.75.75.75z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Screenshot coming soon</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <!-- Main content -->
          <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-10">

            <!-- Problem -->
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-5 bg-[#02066F] rounded-full inline-block"></span>
                The Problem
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Built a full-stack web application that allows administrators to manage a movie catalog and moderate user-submitted reviews. The challenge was to provide a secure, role-based platform where critics can write and score reviews, and admins have visibility into platform activity through a centralized dashboard — while also supporting soft-deletion of movies and image uploads.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Role -->
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-5 bg-[#02066F] rounded-full inline-block"></span>
                My Role
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Sole developer. Designed and implemented the full application including:</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-2">
                <% [
                  "Data models (Movie, Review, Genre, Rating, UserProfile) with EF Core migrations",
                  "Role and user seeding services for Admin/Critic setup",
                  "Admin dashboard with aggregate stats — total movies, reviews, average score, top genres",
                  "CRUD for movies with soft-delete support (IsDeleted, DeletedAt)",
                  "Review management with publish/unpublish control and score validation (0–5)",
                  "Azure Blob Storage integration for movie poster uploads",
                  "External REST API integration via HttpClient (MovieApiService)",
                  "Cookie-based authentication with custom login and access-denied routes"
                ].forEach(item => { %>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[#6B72FF] mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span>
                    <%= item %>
                  </li>
                <% }) %>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Outcome -->
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-5 bg-[#02066F] rounded-full inline-block"></span>
                Outcome
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Delivered a fully functional multi-role movie review platform with a working admin dashboard, secure authentication, external API integration, and cloud image storage — demonstrating end-to-end full-stack ASP.NET Core development with both EF Core and Dapper for data access.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>

          <!-- Sidebar -->
          <div class="space-y-6">

            <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-4">Tech Stack</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <% [
                  "ASP.NET Core MVC",".NET","C#",
                  "Entity Framework Core","Dapper","SQL Server",
                  "ASP.NET Core Identity","Azure Blob Storage","Azurite",
                  "HttpClient","Bootstrap","Razor Views"
                ].forEach(t => { %>
                  <span class="bg-[#02066F]/30 text-[#8B8FFF] text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border border-[#02066F]"><%= t %></span>
                <% }) %>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-4">Highlights</h3>
              <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#6B72FF]">✓</span> Multi-role auth (Admin, Critic)</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#6B72FF]">✓</span> Admin dashboard with stats</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#6B72FF]">✓</span> Soft-delete for movies</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#6B72FF]">✓</span> Azure Blob image uploads</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#6B72FF]">✓</span> External REST API integration</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#6B72FF]">✓</span> EF Core + Dapper dual ORM</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-gray-800 py-6 text-center text-sm text-gray-600">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Mahit KC. Built with Express v5 &amp; Tailwind CSS v4.
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
